{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-templates-post-template-tsx","path":"/blog/2022/01/2022-01-08-webassembly/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"홍승아 기술 블로그","description":"홍승아 기술 블로그에 오신걸 환영합니다.","author":"홍승아","type":"website","siteUrl":"https://seungahhong.github.io","social":{"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/people/%ED%99%8D%EC%8A%B9%EC%95%84/100002349562000/","github":"https://github.com/seungahhong","notion":"https://material-debt-c1c.notion.site/daa60481e37840ea9e1b7e1b12269942","linkedin":"https://www.linkedin.com/in/seungahhong/"}}},"allFile":{"edges":[{"node":{"name":"facebook","publicURL":"/static/b185e9b61bb465d92b14ed1c9a9ded61/facebook.svg","childImageSharp":null}},{"node":{"name":"github","publicURL":"/static/4a6687a74051de2b3536e95d0b6c992a/github.svg","childImageSharp":null}},{"node":{"name":"linkedin","publicURL":"/static/3dc9e0d0f748678205218f1c72941cc2/linkedin.svg","childImageSharp":null}},{"node":{"name":"notion","publicURL":"/static/19b0f81386812ed2f2f3a7aea202935f/notion.svg","childImageSharp":null}},{"node":{"name":"background","publicURL":"/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/background.jpg","childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/c2a83/background.jpg","srcSet":"/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/9330e/background.jpg 139w,\n/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/53b4d/background.jpg 278w,\n/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/c2a83/background.jpg 555w","sizes":"(min-width: 555px) 555px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/3ee68/background.webp 139w,\n/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/d0ff1/background.webp 278w,\n/static/77f5c833c2343c992fd263c780495905/21b9c/background.webp 555w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 555px) 555px, 100vw"}]},"width":555,"height":961}}}}]},"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"웹어셈블리-나온-이유\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%96%B4%EC%85%88%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AC-%EB%82%98%EC%98%A8-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\" aria-label=\"웹어셈블리 나온 이유 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹어셈블리 나온 이유</h2>\n<p>구글의 <a href=\"https://developer.chrome.com/native-client\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">NaCI</a>(Native Client), 모질라의 <a href=\"http://asmjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">asm.js</a>(JavaScript 서브셋) 등 네이티브 머신 코드를 웹으로 가져오기 위한, 그리고 빠르게 실행하기 위한 시도들은 결과적으로 웹어셈블리(이하 ‘wasm’으로 표기)로 귀결되면서 개발이 시작되었다.</p>\n<p>2019년 12월, W3C는 현재 <a href=\"https://webassembly.github.io/spec/core/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">1.1 버전</a> 상태인 wsam를 HTML, CSS 그리고 JavaScript에 이어 웹의 4번째 언어로 공식 권고함</p>\n<h2 id=\"웹어셈블리-구동방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%96%B4%EC%85%88%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AC-%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"웹어셈블리 구동방식 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹어셈블리 구동방식</h2>\n<p>JavaScript 엔진 내에서 JavaScript 코드와 wasm의 실행 과정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>컴파일된 바이너리 포맷의 wasm 모듈은 JavaScript를 대신하거나 JavaScript 내에서 실행되지 않고, JavaScript와 같이 JavaScript 엔진 내에서 나란히 실행</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/4423c/Untitled.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.328125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/4fae8/Untitled.webp 256w,\n/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/2bf0f/Untitled.webp 512w,\n/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/d71bc/Untitled.webp 1024w,\n/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/57ca4/Untitled.webp 1036w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/e3135/Untitled.png 256w,\n/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/06341/Untitled.png 512w,\n/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/42a19/Untitled.png 1024w,\n/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/4423c/Untitled.png 1036w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/084af5d495afaddcaad3f44d8a9fd02e/42a19/Untitled.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Emscripten은 C/C++ 코드를 가져와 LLVM을 통해 전달하고 LLVM 생성 바이트 코드를 JavaScript(특히 JavaScript의 하위 집합인 Asm.js)로 변환합니다.</p>\n<p>WASM 생성과정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>C,C++ → [Clang툴(LLVM) → LLVM 바이트코드 생성 → Asm.js 변환]: Emscripten</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1yoy1Fal.png\" alt=\"http://i.imgur.com/1yoy1Fal.png\"></p>\n<p>emscripten 변천</p>\n<ol>\n<li>wasm 컴파일은 <a href=\"https://github.com/emscripten-core/emscripten-fastcomp/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">fastcomp</a>(LLVM plus Emscripten’s asm.js backend)가 백엔드를 담당</li>\n<li>C/C++을 컴파일해 중간 표현식(IR)</li>\n<li>fastcomp를 통해 asm.js로 컴파일</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/binaryen/blob/master/src/asm2wasm.h\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">asm2wasm</a>을 사용해 wasm으로 이어지는 컴파일 파이프라인</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/a8177/Untitled3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 23.4375%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/4fae8/Untitled3.webp 256w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/2bf0f/Untitled3.webp 512w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/d71bc/Untitled3.webp 1024w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/f3efb/Untitled3.webp 1536w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/598c0/Untitled3.webp 1710w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/e3135/Untitled3.png 256w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/06341/Untitled3.png 512w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/42a19/Untitled3.png 1024w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/e8464/Untitled3.png 1536w,\n/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/a8177/Untitled3.png 1710w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/7f10f743fcb6dc8d74cd3f6cd0c2d7fd/42a19/Untitled3.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled3\"\n            title=\"Untitled3\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>V8 팀은 Emscripten에서 불필요한 asm.js 컴파일 과정을 거치지 않고, 네이티브 LLVM wasm 백엔드가 기본 파이프라인이 되도록 개선해 많은 영역에서 성능 개선을 이뤄냈다고 밝혔다.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/v8js/status/1145704863377981445\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://twitter.com/v8js/status/1145704863377981445</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"wasm을-왜-사용하는걸까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#wasm%EC%9D%84-%EC%99%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%EA%B1%B8%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"wasm을 왜 사용하는걸까 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>wasm을 왜 사용하는걸까?</h2>\n<p>JavaScript 엔진의 단계별 작업 과정</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/200b8/Untitled1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.171875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/4fae8/Untitled1.webp 256w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/2bf0f/Untitled1.webp 512w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/d71bc/Untitled1.webp 1024w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/f3efb/Untitled1.webp 1536w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/96d48/Untitled1.webp 2048w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/bf5d1/Untitled1.webp 3064w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/e3135/Untitled1.png 256w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/06341/Untitled1.png 512w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/42a19/Untitled1.png 1024w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/e8464/Untitled1.png 1536w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/2eb59/Untitled1.png 2048w,\n/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/200b8/Untitled1.png 3064w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/929eb713d855b0bd4c29948c98a6f6e0/42a19/Untitled1.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h3 id=\"fetching\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fetching\" aria-label=\"fetching permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Fetching</h3>\n<p>실행할 모듈/코드를 로딩하는 과정</p>\n<p>⇒ wasm은 바이너리 파일임으로, 자바스크립트 minify, magling을 하더라도 로딩속도는 향상</p>\n<h3 id=\"parse\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#parse\" aria-label=\"parse permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Parse</h3>\n<p>다운로드한 소스 코드를 파싱해 인터프리터가 이해할 수 있도록 만드는 과정</p>\n<p>Javacript: JS → AST → Javascript 엔진 이해할 수 있는 바이트코드 생성 → 실행</p>\n<p>WSAM: LLVM을 통한 중간표현식(asm.js) → 디코딩, 오류여부 파악 → 실행</p>\n<h3 id=\"compile--optimize\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#compile--optimize\" aria-label=\"compile  optimize permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Compile + Optimize</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>기준 및 최적화 컴파일러를 통해 컴파일되는 과정</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Javascript : <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Just-in-time_compilation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">JIT</a>(Just-In-Time) 컴파일러를 통해 실행되는 동안 컴파일이 동시에 이뤄</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 1024px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/d98b8/Untitled2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 38.67187499999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n          <source\n              srcset=\"/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/4fae8/Untitled2.webp 256w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/2bf0f/Untitled2.webp 512w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/d71bc/Untitled2.webp 1024w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/f3efb/Untitled2.webp 1536w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/87c42/Untitled2.webp 1588w\"\n              sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n              type=\"image/webp\"\n            />\n          <source\n            srcset=\"/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/e3135/Untitled2.png 256w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/06341/Untitled2.png 512w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/42a19/Untitled2.png 1024w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/e8464/Untitled2.png 1536w,\n/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/d98b8/Untitled2.png 1588w\"\n            sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\"\n            type=\"image/png\"\n          />\n          <img\n            class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n            src=\"/static/da93a24a276a3da229bbe3232617f4c1/42a19/Untitled2.png\"\n            alt=\"Untitled\"\n            title=\"Untitled\"\n            loading=\"lazy\"\n            decoding=\"async\"\n            style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n          />\n        </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>WSAM</p>\n<ol>\n<li>wasm 자체는 기계어에 가까우며, 명시적 타입(32 bit와 64 bit Float와 Integer로 구성된 <a href=\"https://webassembly.github.io/spec/core/syntax/types.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">4가지 원시 타입</a> - f32, f64, i32, i64)이 사용</li>\n<li>JS 엔진 컴파일 시 타입체킹X</li>\n<li>LLVM을 통해 여러 가지 최적화가 적용된 상태이므로, 컴파일과 최적화에 많은 작업을 수행할 필요가 없다.</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"re-optimize\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#re-optimize\" aria-label=\"re optimize permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Re-optimize</h3>\n<p>JIT 컴파일러의 예측이 틀렸을 때 재최적화하거나 최적화 코드를 구제해 다시 기준 코드로 전달하는 재조정 과정</p>\n<ul>\n<li>이전 변수의 타입이 직전 반복과 다른 경우, 다시 최적화가 필요한 경우</li>\n<li>WSAM: 최적화 상태이고, 타입에 대한 체크가 필요없어 재최적화 사이크 불필요</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"execute\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#execute\" aria-label=\"execute permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Execute</h3>\n<p>코드의 실행</p>\n<p>WSAM : 컴파일러를 타겟으로 디자인되어 있어 컴파일러 최적화된 결과물을 출력</p>\n<p>Javascript: 최적화된 코드사용은 개발자의 역량에 의존</p>\n<h3 id=\"gc\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#gc\" aria-label=\"gc permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>GC</h3>\n<p>할당되었지만 더는 사용되지 않는 메모리 영역을 해제하는 과정</p>\n<p>WSAM: 메모리 생성,해제를 명시적으로 해주고 있기 때문에 GC가 불필요하다.</p>\n<p>그외에 좋아진 점</p>\n<p>사용 메모리 확장(2GB -> 4GB)</p>\n<p>데이터 공유(web worker간 데이터 공유 → ShareArrayBuffer),</p>\n<p>→ c++ pthread 이용해서 ipc 통신 가능</p>\n<p>…</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://d2.naver.com/helloworld/8257914\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://d2.naver.com/helloworld/8257914</a></p>\n<h1 id=\"웹어셈블리는-어디에-사용되나\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%96%B4%EC%85%88%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AC%EB%8A%94-%EC%96%B4%EB%94%94%EC%97%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%90%98%EB%82%98\" aria-label=\"웹어셈블리는 어디에 사용되나 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>웹어셈블리는 어디에 사용되나?</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://madewithwebassembly.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://madewithwebassembly.com/</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"예제코드를-살펴볼까\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%B4%ED%8E%B4%EB%B3%BC%EA%B9%8C\" aria-label=\"예제코드를 살펴볼까 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>예제코드를 살펴볼까??</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://frontdev.tistory.com/entry/Rust%EB%A1%9C-SPA-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0-1-%EB%A6%AC%EC%8A%A4%ED%8A%B8-%EB%A7%8C%EB%93%A4%EA%B8%B0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://frontdev.tistory.com/entry/Rust로-SPA-만들기-1-리스트-만들기</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"rust\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#rust\" aria-label=\"rust permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Rust</h3>\n<p>Yew:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://webassembly.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">WebAssembly를</a> 사용하여 다중 스레드 프론트 엔드 웹 앱을 만들기 위한 최신 <a href=\"https://www.rust-lang.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">Rust</a> 프레임워크</p>\n<p>DOM API 호출을 최소화</p>\n<p>wasm_bindgen</p>\n<p>js engine ↔ 웹어셈블리는 숫자타입만 지원가능(그외에 타입을 지원하기 위해서 추가)</p>\n<p>JavaScript 파일은 Rust를 호출할 때 사용될 인터페이스 역할</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"rust\"><pre class=\"language-rust\"><code class=\"language-rust\">export function <span class=\"token function\">greet</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>s<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> string<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// rust -> js</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> rust <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">import</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"./wasm_greet\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// js -> rust</span>\nrust<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">then</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>m <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> m<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">greet</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"World!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"http://lib.rs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">lib.rs</a> → rust에서 실행파일은 <a href=\"http://main.rs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">main.rs</a>, 라이브러리로 생성 시 lib.rs 생성(cargo new –lib [프로젝트명])</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://mod.rs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">mod.rs</a> → javscript index.js</p>\n<p>문법</p>\n<p>mod → javascript import</p>\n<p>pub → typescript publish</p>\n<p>use → import { Home } from ‘home’ 동일</p>\n<p>type → typescript type</p>\n<p>→ 빌드 시 _bg.wasm 최적화된 코드로 변경</p>\n<p>참고사항</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://johnresig.com/blog/asmjs-javascript-compile-target/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://johnresig.com/blog/asmjs-javascript-compile-target/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://m.blog.naver.com/z1004man/221914280533\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://m.blog.naver.com/z1004man/221914280533</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://d2.naver.com/helloworld/8257914\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://d2.naver.com/helloworld/8257914</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tech.kakao.com/2021/05/17/frontend-growth-08/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://tech.kakao.com/2021/05/17/frontend-growth-08/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://ui.toast.com/weekly-pick/ko_20180411\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://ui.toast.com/weekly-pick/ko_20180411</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"webassembly","date":"2022.01.08","category":"개발","tags":["webassembly"]},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%96%B4%EC%85%88%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AC-%EB%82%98%EC%98%A8-%EC%9D%B4%EC%9C%A0\">웹어셈블리 나온 이유</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%96%B4%EC%85%88%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AC-%EA%B5%AC%EB%8F%99%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\">웹어셈블리 구동방식</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#wasm%EC%9D%84-%EC%99%9C-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%EA%B1%B8%EA%B9%8C\">wasm을 왜 사용하는걸까?</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#fetching\">Fetching</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#parse\">Parse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#compile--optimize\">Compile + Optimize</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#re-optimize\">Re-optimize</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#execute\">Execute</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#gc\">GC</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%9B%B9%EC%96%B4%EC%85%88%EB%B8%94%EB%A6%AC%EB%8A%94-%EC%96%B4%EB%94%94%EC%97%90-%EC%82%AC%EC%9A%A9%EB%90%98%EB%82%98\">웹어셈블리는 어디에 사용되나?</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C%EC%BD%94%EB%93%9C%EB%A5%BC-%EC%82%B4%ED%8E%B4%EB%B3%BC%EA%B9%8C\">예제코드를 살펴볼까??</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#rust\">Rust</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/2022/01/2022-01-08-webassembly/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2022/01/2022-01-09-graphql/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"graphql"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/blog/2021/12/2021-12-31-mobx/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"mobx"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["4157816502"]}